text: Antonio Narciso Luna de San Pedro y Novicio Ancheta (; October 29, 1866 – June 5, 1899) was a Filipino army general and a pharmacist. He fought in the Philippine–American War before his assassination on June 5, 1899, at the age of 32. ==References== Category:1866 births Category:1899 deaths Category:Filipino generals Category:People from Manila Category:Assassinated people
title: Antonio Luna
